sentences.sentence: I have a hard time with electronica.

sentences.sentence: Turning the electronica up a notch the upbeat march of the icons is a glamorous walk down a fashion runway.
sentences.translation: 欢快的《巨像进行曲》就像是辉煌的t型台音乐，它为电子乐加了漂亮的一分。
